snippet.title: Fallout: Nuevo México - Official Gameplay Trailer Part: 1 | "New Mexico"
snippet.description:
Welcome to the Land of Enchantment. The year is 2166 - 5 years after the events of "Fallout: A Post Nuclear Role-Playing Game." Every choice made will revolutionize the future for better or worse. Built on the Fallout: New Vegas engine, this free full-on RPG based Modification brings you a brand-new Fallout experience. 

DISCLAIMER:
Everything shown in this footage is bound to change and is considered final until the full modification game is released.

We are not affiliated with Bethesda Game Studios, Obsidian Entertainment and any associated affiliates - we operate solely as the "Nuevo Mexico Team."
      
Support Us:
